  "subject": "[GLOBAL] Create a gitlab-ci YAML conf from tox.ini",
  "commit_message": "[GLOBAL] Create a gitlab-ci YAML conf from tox.ini\n\n- add a gitlab-ci YAML configuration file\n- configure a tox:defaults profile\n  that performs all jobs declared in tox.ini envlist\n- script in it the install of necessary packages\n- enable tox jobs concurrency (tox -p auto) in it\n  this shifts tox classical display to a quieter one\n  (\"-o\" can be used to restore the classical display: \"tox -p auto -o\")\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-2643\nSigned-off-by: guillaume.lambert <guillaume.lambert@orange.com>\nChange-Id: Id12e44f920829ccf6b66c619338247b03696aefe\n",
